<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="please-int">please <strong><em>int</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pliːz/    美 /pliːz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[表示有礼貌地请求对方] 请；好吗：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Would / Could / Will you please …?
你……好吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[表示礼貌地接受] 好；谢谢：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Would you like some more?
还要来点吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Yes, please.
好的，谢谢。</p><footer>2013 四川</footer></div></div>